{
  "texts": [
    "[35] The study protocol was uploaded to the OSF prior to running the initial search and updates after the search have been documented (see Appendix 2 for the anonymized protocol).",
    "Search strategy and selection criteriaSearches were conducted in the following four online databases: PubMed, PsycINFO, Cochrane, and Web of Science.",
    "Backward and forward citation searching was manually conducted using the Web of Science.",
    "The search was carried out in June 2024.",
    "Articles published before June 6, 2024, and that met the inclusion criteria were included in the review.The search terms used were a combination of the population (i.e., patients on the waiting lists for psychotherapy), treatment (i.e., intervention), and outcome (i.e., depression and/or anxiety)."
  ]
}